<time  itemprop="commentTime" datetime="2015-02-03T16:57Z">FEB 3, 2015</time></h2>
<p itemprop="commentText">
The structural funds inside the EU (with Greece as main recipient) have actually been multiple Marshall plans. <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
